UNgqongqoshe angenza, ngesaziso kuGazethi, anikeze isikhathi esiphezulu sezimvumelwano zomthengi zesikhathi esigcwele, ngokujwayelekile, noma ngezigaba ezibekiwe zezivumelwano;
IKhomishana ingasungula, noma ihloniphe njengegunya, irejista lapho noma yimuphi umuntu angabhalisa khona ibhulogi langaphambili, ngokujwayelekile noma ngezinhloso ezithile, ngokumelene nanoma yikuphi ukuxhumana okuyinhloko ngenjongo yokuthengisa ngokuqondile.
Isimiso sesikhathi sokuxhumana nabathengi
noma ukwamukela kumthengi noma yiziphi izimpahla ezinikezwe ngokwemisebenzi;
Lesi sigaba asisebenzi ekuthengisweni uma isigaba 44 soMthetho wezokuThintana nokuThengiswa kwe-elekthronikhi sisebenza kulowo msebenzi.
